## Examples

### Before (Markdown Table)

```markdown
| Technology | Keywords | Agent | Score |
|------------|----------|-------|-------|
| React Native | react-native, expo | mobile-react-native | +60 |
| Flutter | flutter, dart | mobile-flutter | +60 |
```

### After (TOON Format)

```toon
tech[2]{technology,keywords,agent,score}:
 React Native,react-native/expo,mobile-react-native,+60
 Flutter,flutter/dart,mobile-flutter,+60
```

### Nested Objects (YAML-style)

```toon
config:
 task: Build feature
 priority: high
 tags[3]: frontend,testing,urgent
```

