## Usage in Aura Frog

All `.mdc` files in this project use TOON format for tables where applicable. When adding new rules or documentation:

1. Use TOON for any table with 3+ rows
2. Use `[N]` count matching actual row count
3. Use `/` separator for multiple values in a field
4. Wrap in ```toon code blocks for syntax highlighting

